com.facebook.buck.rules

Class TargetNode<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.rules.TargetNode<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasBuildTarget, java.lang.Comparable<TargetNode<?>>

    public class TargetNode<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<TargetNode<?>>, HasBuildTarget
    A TargetNode represents a node in the target graph which is created by the Parser as a result of parsing BUCK files in a project. It is responsible for processing the raw (python) inputs of a build rule, and gathering any build targets and paths referenced from those inputs.
